data.description: **Boyertown Twin close to town. ** Welcome to this charming twin home located in the highly sought-after Boyertown School District! This three-story gem offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, making it an ideal residence for your next chapter.  Location: Situated just one block from Main Street, this home provides easy access to the heart of the community. Enjoy the convenience of local shops, restaurants, and entertainment options right at your doorstep. With the post office conveniently located across the street, you'll appreciate the ease of managing your mail and staying connected.  Bedrooms: Featuring three spacious bedrooms, this home provides ample space for your family or guests. Each bedroom is designed with comfort in mind, and one of them boasts a private balcony, offering a peaceful retreat for relaxation.  Layout: Spread across three stories, this twin home offers a well-thought-out floor plan. The multi-level design provides a sense of openness and flexibility, allowing you to tailor the space to your lifestyle. The layout is perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones.  Basement: A full basement adds valuable storage space.   Proximity: The proximity to Main Street means you're just steps away from local attractions, events, and community gatherings. Enjoy the vibrant atmosphere of the neighborhood while maintaining the peace and privacy of your own home.  Additional Features:  Full basement for storage or customization Convenient balcony off one of the bedrooms Proximity to local amenities and Main Street Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful twin home yours. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm and convenience of living in the heart of Boyertown!
